YOUR SPEECH, OKAY?

22:27.714 --> 22:29.882
-TEACHER: WE'RE GONNA DO
SOME SPEECH WORK.

22:29.982 --> 22:31.350
-NICE WORK.

22:31.451 --> 22:33.786
-[CHILDREN TALKING]

22:37.390 --> 22:39.926
-SIGN LANGUAGE IS MORE THAN
FINGER SPELLING AND GESTURES.

22:40.026 --> 22:42.429
IT'S ABOUT TOTAL VISUAL
COMMUNICATION

22:42.529 --> 22:43.996
USING MIND,

22:44.096 --> 22:46.466
FACIAL EXPRESSION
AND BODY LANGUAGE.

22:47.033 --> 22:50.169
A CHANGE OF EXPRESSION CAN
ALTER THE ENTIRE MEANING
OF A SIGN.

22:50.269 --> 22:53.172
