OVER THERE DOING?

23:16.028 --> 23:17.697
-THEY'RE HAVING
A VOCABULARY LESSON.

23:18.164 --> 23:20.166
MANY SIGNS ARE
REALLY VISUAL DEPICTIONS

23:20.266 --> 23:22.101
OF WHAT THEY REPRESENT.

23:22.201 --> 23:24.236
THE HAWAIIANS HAVE BEEN
DOING IT FOR CENTURIES
WHEN THEY DANCE THE HULA.

23:25.071 --> 23:27.239
-AND WHAT ABOUT
THOSE CHILDREN OVER THERE?

23:27.339 --> 23:29.576
-THEY'RE LEARNING HOW
TO MODULATE THEIR VOICES.

