THIS IS IT, DUDES AND DUDESSES.

35:03.068 --> 35:04.670
BIG MONDAY
HAS ARRIVED.

35:04.770 --> 35:07.939
SOME BEACHES ARE ALREADY
REPORTING EIGHT-FOOT SETS.

35:08.039 --> 35:12.611
