ONLY KANALOA KNOWS FOR SURE.

35:37.569 --> 35:39.137
-MORNING, DAD.
WHAT'S FOR BREAKFAST?

35:39.238 --> 35:40.339
-OATMEAL.

35:41.373 --> 35:42.441
BIG DAY TODAY.

35:42.541 --> 35:44.243
-BIG MONDAY.
-THAT'S RIGHT.

35:44.343 --> 35:46.144
WHAT DO YOU SAY YOU SPEND
THE DAY WITH YOUR OLD MAN,
EH?

35:46.245 --> 35:48.814
-I KIND OF PLANNED ON GOING
TO THE BEACH WITH MY FRIENDS.

35:48.914 --> 35:50.516
-OH, COME ON, PAL.

35:50.616 --> 35:52.117
COULD USE YOUR HELP.
WAVES ARE GONNA BE
OUTRAGEOUS.

35:52.218 --> 35:54.320
WE'LL BE PULLING
'EM OUT LIKE TUNA.
-NO THANKS.

35:54.420 --> 35:55.921
-WELL, TO TELL YOU THE TRUTH,
I MISS YOU.

35:56.488 --> 35:57.823
I WOULD LIKE TO SPEND
A DAY WITH MY SON.

35:57.923 --> 35:59.691
OKAY?

35:59.791 --> 36:01.327
-YOU'RE SCARED TO LET ME GO
TO THE BEACH BY MYSELF,
AREN'T YOU?

36:01.427 --> 36:03.195
-I DON'T WANT YOU GOING
IN THE WATER TODAY.

36:03.295 --> 36:04.430
THAT'S FOR SURE.

36:04.530 --> 36:06.298
-YOU TOLD ME TO OVERCOME
MY FEARS.

36:06.932 --> 36:08.700
AND WHAT BETTER TIME
THAN TODAY?

36:08.800 --> 36:10.402
-HOBIE, NO.

36:10.502 --> 36:12.471
NOW, YOU WANNA GO
TO THE BEACH WITH
YOUR FRIENDS, THAT'S FINE.

36:12.571 --> 36:14.005
BUT YOU SEE THAT?

36:14.105 --> 36:15.507
STAYS HERE.

36:34.293 --> 36:36.395
-SO WHERE'S YOUR BOARD, CHICKEN?

36:37.496 --> 36:39.097
-I'M NOT SCARED, CLAY.

36:39.197 --> 36:40.666
I'M JUST NOT STUPID.

36:40.766 --> 36:42.734
YOU DON'T HAVE ANYTHING
TO PROVE EITHER.

36:42.834 --> 36:46.538
CLAY, THEY'RE GETTING
EVERYBODY OUT OF THE WATER.

36:46.638 --> 36:48.540
NOBODY WILL
THINK YOU'RE CHICKEN.

36:48.640 --> 36:50.909
-YOU BETTER BELIEVE
THEY WON'T.

37:43.194 --> 37:44.796
-GET A LIFEGUARD HERE, NOW!

37:45.331 --> 37:47.533
-[BOYS SHOUTING]

37:59.044 --> 38:00.446
-I WANT EVERYBODY
KEPT OUT OF THE WATER.

38:00.546 --> 38:02.047
SWIMMERS, SURFERS,
EVERYBODY.

38:02.147 --> 38:04.383
-ALL RIGHT, YOU HEARD HIM.
LET'S GET DOWN THERE.

39:55.661 --> 39:57.162
