ALL RIGHT.

40:02.267 --> 40:03.702
-JUST LIE BACK DOWN.

40:05.270 --> 40:07.539
-TOOK A LOT OF GUTS,
WHAT YOU DID OUT THERE.

40:08.574 --> 40:09.975
-I'M REAL PROUD OF YOU.

40:12.077 --> 40:14.045
I'LL NEVER FORGET
WHAT YOU DID TODAY.

40:15.346 --> 40:16.582
OKAY.

40:19.117 --> 40:20.418
-LOOK.

40:33.632 --> 40:36.802
-[CHILDREN CHATTERING]

40:46.745 --> 40:48.046
-WHAT DID SHE SAY?

40:48.780 --> 40:51.850
-SHE SAID,
"I LOVE YOU, MOMMY."

41:06.197 --> 41:07.132
-OH.

41:09.367 --> 41:10.569
SONNY,

41:11.369 --> 41:12.738
THANK YOU VERY MUCH.

41:13.304 --> 41:14.205
IT WORKED,

41:15.073 --> 41:16.708
BUT I DON'T
NEED IT ANYMORE.

41:19.144 --> 41:20.311
-HOBIE,

41:20.879 --> 41:22.480
